chat.msg: hey there, estas listo?
si
genial, estoy en el punto de partida, justo al lado de una ramita que conduce a una isla pequeña con un tigre
¿a dónde debo ir después?
after that we are going to the where the blue and yellow bird is.
Okay, so I should head southwest towards the larger island with the parrot, correct?
yes
perfect! Now I'm on the big island with the parrot in the tree, what's next?
after that there should be a green frog that you would go to next
gotcha! so i’m heading southeast following the three rocks leading to a new island with a frog, correct?
yes
cool, now i see the frog on the new island, where to next?
now you woud head southwest to the crocodile
ah gotcha
venturing west right to the crocodile. what's the next move?
next moe would be crossing the two rocks to get to the giraffe
alright, so i'm skipping to the large island with our tall friend, the giraffe
what's my next move from the giraffe?
you head east to the snake and the treasure should be right next to it
got it! heading southeast from the giraffe to the snake then
hey, i see the treasure 2 steps to the east of our slithery friend! *finished*
hola, q tal? ready to play?
HI si estoy listo
genial! vamos a empezar. desde donde estás, el perro blanco, camina unos pasos hacia la izquierda, hacia el banco de madera
cruzarás un sendero hacia el puesto de flores, pero no llegues allí. ¿llegaste al sendero?
yes i am by the flowers now
perfect! now make a 180 degree turn to the left
You are going to cross the path again towards the white dog. do you follow me?
yes now we would cross the log to get to the bridge where people are riding nikes
not quite! we're going to cross over the branch first, heading south
let's aim for the other white dog next to the picnic. got it?
yes i was already there now do we cross the next branch?
not yet! go over the picnic mat here, touch the bowl of berries, then continue west
good so far?
yes
awesome! now, let's cross that branch over the river, going north
are you with me?
yes
great. once you've crossed, don't touch the green bush
circle it from the right until you reach the florist stand. can you see it?
yes
perfect, now turn left (west), go under the stand, and you'll find a big bridge with two folks riding bikes
got there?
yes
lovely! now, keep moving west, passing the bridge
ok
excellent! just past the bridge, you'll spot two elderly people reading newspapers on a bench
see them?
yes
cool! now move southwards, just a few steps, between the old folks and another branch
you should reach a green bush near the end of the branch
yes
perfect! now let's go east, between the branch and the bush
here
awesome! a few steps to the east and you should be seeing something
what do you see?
deer
bingo! you've made it
well done!
great
awesome! that was really fun, wasn't it? do you want to go for another round?
hey there, estas listo?
yes
cool! i'm at the tent up north
where to now?
you head south until you see a dog
spotted the dog here, sitting next to a fire
what's my next move?
head east next to the cr and mushrooms
got it, at the red mushroom and blue car now
what's next, captain?
head south to the telescope
alright, made it to the telescope
what's the next step?
head a little west an you should see a cabin
easy peasy, i'm by the house with the rocks
*finished*. fun game!
hey, estas listo?
yes
great! start by walking under the first palm tree
take a right, cross the second tree, then make a sharp left before you reach the third one. head south!
ok
cool! up next, you'll see a cute brown puppy
pass it to the left, turn a little to the left and then straight to the south you go
ok whats next
see those rocks up ahead? navigate between the big one on your left and the small one on your right
your destination is the ocean
ok
time for some water fun! move in, you'll see a big red crab
hang a right and skim the big rock, keep going west
ok
keep going until you spot a medium rock, and a shark in the water, scary! but, no worries, just make a sharp right turn
im next to the rock and volley ball
perfect! now, head back to land, squeeze between that rock and the colorful ball, then continue north
ok dne
good job! now, look slightly to your left and head north-west
you will see a red tent to your left and a big speaker to your right. go between them
ok
now, circle around that red tent, like you're hugging it
then head back south towards the sea
ok
stop just before you hit the water, then turn right and shimmy below the red kayak
ok
awesome! now make a quick 90-degree turn to the right and move along the kayak
ok
you're almost there
keep going until you reach a small, green bush. you've made it! good job, mate!
